The mansion of the imperial executive. Esuka, who
was captured, was kept as a pet by the residents
of this house.

Hohoho... She's a bit of a mischievous pup, but
she's just right for my son.
Hey! Hey! You're slow, stupid dog!

(This... this brat... If I manage to escape, I'll
definitely punch him...!)

In addition to her body being controlled by
prosthetics, Esuka's vocal cords had been
modified, leaving her only able to imitate the
sound of a dog.

Papa! I'm going to bring Pess, so please take care
of her for a bit.
Well, well, I'll help with the training too. Sit.

Hohoho, she's become quite skilled at performing
tricks.

(This... this perverted bastard! I'll remember
this...)
(Wha, what's with this ridiculously large dog?)

The creature referred to as Pess was the Empire's
biological weapon, Bio Orthros, capable of
everything from guarding VIPs to eliminating
suspicious individuals.
(Wha, what is this stupid dog doing!)
Huh, Pess seems to be acting strange, doesn't he?

Hmm? Is he getting excited by the scent of a
female?
Ahahaha! This guy wants to mate!
Kyaa! Kyaa, kyaa! (Stop it, I said!)
(Uuuu! This is the worst, the worst, the worst!)
Hahaha! Isn't their compatibility quite good?

(Th-this stupid dog's... just purely violent
mating, I-I'm not feeling anything...)
(N-no... this is... just like a real dog...!)

(Ah...no...my body...is succumbing to a strong
male...)

What's this, what's this, has Pess's cock caught
your fancy?

(There's no way I can win against such rough and
powerful mating...)

Wow, you two are getting along so well already! I
wonder if you could reproduce.
